# JWKSet.Keys

**Dictionary**

An object that defines a single JSON Web Key.

## Declaration

```swift
object JWKSet.Keys
```

## Overview

JWK is an open standard ([https://www.rfc-editor.org/rfc/rfc7517]) that defines a data structure to represent cryptographic keys.
